<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coffee Machine - Premium Coffee Experience</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:ital,wght@0,200..800;1,200..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .landing-container {
            text-align: center;
            color: #222222;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #fe242d;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
        }

        .brand-name {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fe242d;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #222222;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .loading-bar {
            width: 300px;
            height: 6px;
            background: #ebebeb;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .loading-progress {
            height: 100%;
            background: #fe242d;
            border-radius: 3px;
            animation: loading 3s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes loading {
            0% { width: 0%; }
            100% { width: 100%; }
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .coffee-icons {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20%;
            left: 10%;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #fe242d;
            opacity: 0.3;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .coffee-icons.right {
            left: auto;
            right: 10%;
            animation-delay: 1.5s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }

        .welcome-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fe242d 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(254, 36, 45, 0.2);
        }

        .welcome-text h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .welcome-text p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .brand-name {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .tagline {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .loading-bar {
                width: 250px;
            }

            .welcome-text {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .welcome-text h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="coffee-icons">
        <i class="fas fa-coffee"></i>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-coffee"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="brand-name">COFFEE MACHINE</h1>
        </div>

        <p class="tagline">Discover the perfect brew for your perfect moment</p>

        <div class="welcome-text">
            <h2>Welcome to Coffee Machine</h2>
            <p>Explore our premium collection of coffee machines, from automatic espresso makers to manual pour-over systems. Find the perfect machine for your coffee journey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="loading-bar">
            <div class="loading-progress"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="subtitle">Preparing your coffee experience...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="coffee-icons right">
        <i class="fas fa-mug-hot"></i>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Auto redirect after 3 seconds
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.href = '/listing';
        }, 5000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>